Description: An Unparalleled ViewSkyfall Lounge, located adjacent to Rivea, is a multi-sensory experience; combining a panoramic overlook of the city, dramatic interiors, chill out sounds, creative plates and artisan cocktails. Enjoy the pace of our laid back atmosphere, a carefree escape from the noise and stress of the city while our resident DJ_s spin easygoing tunes and eclectic beats
Location: 3940 S Las Vegas Blvd, Las Vegas, NV 89119
